classDiagram
    note "FoundrySpec: AI-First Collaboration"
    
    class AIAgent {
        +String role "Primary Operator"
        +scaffoldProject()
        +createInitialSpecs()
        +readCodebase()
        +generateAsIsSpecs()
        +identifyAmbiguity()
        +implementFeatures()
    }

    class HumanArchitect {
        +String role "Strategic Visionary"
        +initializeGreenfield()
        +defineIntent()
        +resolveAmbiguity()
        +approveSpecs()
    }

    class FoundrySpecCLI {
        +String role "The Enabler"
        +scaffold(init)
        +build()
        +serve()
        +addCategory()
        +upgradeTemplates()
        +pullExternalSpecs()
        +syncExternalSpecs()
        +scaffoldDeployment()
        +reportChanges()
        +displayHelp()
        +validateIntegrity()
    }

    FoundrySpecCLI <.. AIAgent : Operates
    FoundrySpecCLI <.. HumanArchitect : Reviews Output
    AIAgent -- HumanArchitect : Collaborates
